# vlc

> Cross-platform multimedia player
> More information: https://wiki.videolan.org/Documentation:Command_line/

- Play a file:

`vlc {file something}`

- Play in fullscreen:

`vlc --fullscreen {file something}`

- Play muted:

`vlc --no-audio {file something}`

- Play repeatedly:

`vlc --loop {file something}`

- Play video from a URL:

`vlc {any something}`
